= *Allowed* Licenses

This page lists the various category of *allowed* licenses in separate tables.
That is: *allowed*, if it is allowed for any use and *allowed-fonts*,
*allowed-content*, *allowed-documentation*, or *allowed-firmware*, if it is
allowed only for certain categories of material as described in
xref:license-approval.adoc[License Approval]. This information is generated
from data maintained in the
https://gitlab.com/fedora/legal/fedora-license-data[Fedora License Data]
repository.

